surveystatement.statement: Thank you for taking part in the test. On the following pages, please select which of the two presented stimuli sounds closer to the reference (button above the presented pair). Each stimulus is 15 seconds long and played repeatedly unless you stop. Please use the small rectangular button to play the selected stimulus, and use the large square button above to make your choice (highlighted in green when selected). PLEASE NOTE: the playback button is different from the selection button and highlighted separately, so please check whether what you selected to play does correspond to what you selected as the answer!

interfaceoption.name: scalerange
interfaceoption.errormessage: Please remember to select one stimulus!
